{"1":[[786,863,"Perfect!"],[863,940,"Looking great!"],[1016,1196,"With Lucas' shoot, the magazine's"],[1196,1340,"number will blow pass a million."],[1340,1670,"I know! His last album already got a million."],[1706,1853,"And now he's booked"],[1853,2054,"for the Super Bowl halftime show."],[2066,2306,"The guy is untouchable right now."],[3570,3702,"The Dior suits are wrinkled."],[3702,3884,"I want them pressed in 10 minutes."],[3926,3991,"Of course!"],[4120,4216,"That's who I needed."],[4216,4477,"The trailer from the garage to the side door. Got it?"],[4556,4728,"Oh! Yes! Right away!"],[4770,5036,"Hey! The floors are covered in hairspray."],[5073,5183,"Mop it up while you're at it."],[5239,5359,"Yes! Um, right away."],[5373,5420,"Suit."],[5446,5483,"Garage."],[5623,5646,"Um..."],[5710,5926,"Emily! Where the hell are you?"],[5946,6076,"Did you print out the contract?"],[6089,6196,"Is the inventory list ready?"],[6196,6316,"Yeah, right away. I'm coming."],[6316,6386,"I'll be right there. I've..."],[6463,6636,"Would you watch it, lady?"],[6666,6781,"I'm so sorry."],[6836,6876,"I..."],[8056,8309,"Lucas! You rejected all seven managers"],[8309,8400,"the company assigned you."],[8416,8536,"What are you looking for?"],[8596,8797,"Why are you so much in a rush?"],[8797,8988,"I just haven't made my decision yet."],[9000,9173,"You're the top star in the country."],[9186,9359,"You need someone to manage your calendar,"],[9359,9640,"book events, and clean up your messes!"],[10166,10293,"Oh, have you seen that?"],[10423,10770,"Come on. Isn't he the most handsome man in life?"],[10963,11095,"Why are you so mad? Hey!"],[11106,11464,"And relax! I'm gonna make a decision by sunset!"],[11543,11606,"Excuse me."],[12426,12628,"Well, well. Emily!"],[12656,12861,"Look at you now that Mark's left you."],[12900,13108,"Look at this necklace he bought me."],[13163,13284,"Gorgeous, isn't it?"],[13300,13403,"And you can't even afford"],[13403,13526,"your daughter's school trip."],[13550,13776,"She must be so disappointed in you."],[14026,14303,"You dropped $2,000 on a necklace,"],[14303,14474,"but your daughter has to miss her school trip?"],[14483,14600,"Some father you are."],[14600,14833,"Too bad she can't miss out on your loser genes."],[14866,14966,"Did you forget?"],[14966,15158,"You quit your job to be a full-time mom."],[15186,15287,"You begged me"],[15287,15424,"to stay home and take care of the kids."],[15446,15574,"And now I'm the loser?"],[15574,15709,"How does that work?"],[15736,16012,"Sweetheart, a failure is a failure."],[16013,16180,"You gave up your career for a man."],[16180,16424,"Now you are worthless."],[16428,16476,"Shut up!"],[16543,16610,"You don't get to judge me."],[16610,16743,"You... you home-wrecker!"],[17956,18000,"Hello?"],[18040,18251,"Emily, three scripts to Lucas' villa, right now."],[18251,18383,"He needs to pick a role in thirty minutes."],[18383,18556,"One second late, I'll dock your whole day's pay!"],[18766,18939,"Got it. I'm on my way."],[19716,19943,"Lukiepoo, that white suit"],[19943,20236,"you wore last week was gorgeous."],[20843,21013,"Asshole can't even get the stairs fixed."],[21196,21324,"I'm here with your MV scripts, Mr. Lucas."],[21324,21422,"Can you please read them?"],[22493,22564,"Um..."],[23273,23604,"God, his body should be illegal."],[24143,24219,"It's you."]],"2":[[136,278,"I have your MV's script, Lucas."],[278,389,"Please read them."],[746,823,"Hand it to me."],[1813,1892,"Help! I can't swim!"],[2516,2623,"Throwing yourself at me?"],[2756,2824,"Bold move."],[2946,3033,"Sorry, I'm..."],[3033,3113,"I'm too old for you."],[3360,3486,"Your heart beats so fast."],[3506,3623,"You say you're not interested?"],[4000,4270,"She really doesn't remember me."],[5216,5363,"Yo, yo, yo, what are you doing?"],[5363,5572,"That's like what? Your eighth fail?"],[5589,5850,"If all you can do is write songs, then go home."],[5873,6086,"And with a small town accent like that,"],[6103,6303,"a major label's never gonna hire you."],[6346,6506,"Go back to your cows. Hillbilly."],[6506,6573,"That's enough!"],[6756,6823,"Yes, Emily."],[7459,7759,"They are here because of family connections."],[7896,8193,"You're here because you worked for it."],[8320,8423,"The audience always"],[8423,8647,"remembers the person that works hard."],[8829,8971,"Failure doesn't mean that it's over."],[9059,9113,"Okay?"],[9209,9359,"You came here to prove that you're better, right?"],[9529,9846,"Eight years. Her words burned into me."],[9936,10215,"Because of her, I gave everything."],[10263,10393,"And I made it here."],[10573,10733,"She still sees me as a kid."],[10833,10893,"That's it."],[10953,11073,"As soon as I can make it back"],[11073,11330,"into the world, I'll take my time."],[11413,11803,"Lukiepoo, you were in my dreams again last night."],[11836,12190,"I love you so much. Please, just reply once..."],[12806,12896,"I made a decision."],[12936,13129,"Emily Carter is gonna be the manager."],[13186,13356,"And she will start tomorrow."],[13496,13622,"Fine, it's your call."],[13636,13855,"That crazy fan still sliding in your DMs?"],[13916,14053,"I deleted her messages."],[14096,14303,"Lucas, this is serious."],[14363,14481,"I'm ready to call the cops."],[14526,14607,"Okay."],[14716,14981,"Next message she sends me, I will forward to you."],[15116,15218,"Bring me Emily Carter."]],"3":[[273,486,"Please change into something dry."],[536,843,"Mr. Lucas still needs to see you."],[843,885,"This way."],[890,934,"What?"],[1286,1376,"Perfect."],[1559,1726,"I have an offer for you."],[1776,1840,"Be my manager."],[1996,2133,"I'm not taking the clients right now."],[2133,2182,"It's fine."],[2206,2285,"Five grand,"],[2316,2392,"and bonus."],[2433,2565,"I heard you have a daughter."],[2683,2833,"You can cover her tuition."],[3723,3881,"Honey, can I talk to you about something?"],[4039,4206,"I'm really sorry that we don't have the money"],[4216,4326,"for your observatory trip."],[4360,4433,"Are you mad at me?"],[4606,4929,"I... I know 135 bucks is a lot for us."],[4966,5036,"It's okay, Mom."],[5086,5420,"Honestly, I didn't even really want to go anyway."],[5583,5649,"Okay."],[5723,5832,"What color you take next?"],[6353,6429,"I..."],[6666,7014,"Emily, Lucas requested you, or he walks."],[7016,7305,"If he breaks contract, you're paying the penalty."],[7305,7336,"Me? But I..."],[7336,7412,"Do you know how many people"],[7412,7529,"would kill for this job?"],[7600,7697,"8 AM tomorrow."],[7743,7932,"Don't be late."],[8023,8093,"Yes, sir."],[8856,8940,"Fine."],[9033,9152,"But I want cash"],[9206,9255,"daily."],[9290,9477,"And absolutely no overtime."],[9566,9631,"Deal."],[11033,11273,"So, your first task,"],[11323,11435,"after-sun lotion."],[11713,11822,"Are you serious?"],[11846,11909,"Yeah."],[11936,12096,"A manager should do everything, huh?"],[12376,12448,"Come on."],[12830,12880,"Even it out."],[13473,13869,"The skin is hotter than I thought and... harder too."],[13953,14268,"Such a perfect body is wasted on such an asshole."]],"4":[[570,616,"Perfect."],[693,756,"You passed."],[793,896,"See you on time tomorrow."],[1603,2026,"Hey, I need seven iced Americanos,"],[2026,2303,"all at two degrees difference."],[2303,2413,"Are you going to open a coffee shop?"],[2413,2593,"In one hour, my office."],[2606,2806,"The timer starts now."],[2826,2933,"She forgot me."],[3023,3233,"Might as well charge a little interest."],[3283,3308,"Fair enough."],[3308,3457,"Hey, come in."],[4866,4913,"What?"],[5106,5172,"Tie my shoe."],[5670,5856,"Since she thinks I'm too young,"],[5913,6196,"I'll be as childish as I want."],[6846,6883,"Wait."],[7026,7199,"Go to ML and pick up my suit."],[7203,7483,"Charity gala is at 7 PM tonight."],[7506,7812,"ML? That's like 80 miles there and back."],[7816,7956,"I'll never make it back by 7."],[7976,8170,"Unless you want to risk"],[8170,8369,"breaking the manager contract."],[8703,9016,"Don't push me too far."],[9216,9266,"Hello."],[9273,9491,"Mrs. Carter? Chloe's in trouble."],[9491,9636,"Please come immediately!"]],"5":[[416,470,"Sweetie?"],[523,583,"Are you okay?"],[616,660,"Mom."],[660,726,"Hey."],[736,938,"Look what you did to my grandson!"],[963,1133,"Your daughter did this to him."],[1146,1337,"You will pay for all the medical expenses"],[1393,1526,"and emotional damages."],[1593,1701,"Everything!"],[1746,1964,"Fatherless kids are wild."],[1973,2210,"You owe us three grand today"],[2210,2343,"or else we're suing you."],[2343,2406,"Mm-hmm."],[2700,2746,"Chloe?"],[2806,2913,"Hey, what happened?"],[2976,3134,"They said I have no father"],[3134,3256,"and my mom doesn't want me"],[3256,3496,"because I couldn't afford the observatory trip."],[3553,3675,"And I'm a freak."],[3675,3696,"Hey."],[3696,3894,"They pushed me first."],[4236,4322,"Did you hear that?"],[4336,4503,"Chloe doesn't start fights unprompted."],[4566,4696,"Did you check the cameras or something?"],[4766,4972,"That was a blind spot for the cameras."],[5003,5259,"The school doesn't want a big scandal."],[5270,5526,"Either pay up or according to regulation,"],[5586,5686,"Chloe will be expelled."],[5686,5811,"But it's not her fault."],[5886,6226,"Mrs. Carter, you know how competitive this school is."],[6276,6546,"Keep fighting, it will hurt both of you."],[6936,7072,"Okay, give me a sec, babe, okay?"],[7523,7568,"Mark."],[7840,7916,"Chloe's in trouble."],[8036,8236,"I need $3,000 and I'll pay you back next week."],[8296,8383,"Three grand?"],[8466,8698,"Listen, you produced a liability"],[8703,8823,"and now you want me to pay?"],[8883,8965,"Dream on."],[9003,9109,"She's your daughter, too."],[9300,9445,"How about you spend the night with me"],[9500,9620,"and I might give a discount."],[10203,10286,"Hey, you'll be okay."],[10336,10646,"Fatherless children have no manners."],[10686,10774,"Am I right?"],[10803,11098,"And your mom can't even afford an observatory trip?"],[11136,11419,"I tell ya, you'd be better off looking at the stars"],[11419,11525,"from the garbage dump."],[11593,11683,"Be a good hobby for ya."],[11723,11994,"Who said my daughter is fatherless?"]],"6":[[126,368,"Who said my daughter is fatherless?"],[563,846,"Sorry, I'm late. My flight got delayed."],[940,997,"Who are you?"],[1069,1434,"I am Chloe's dad."],[1556,1593,"What?"],[1593,1715,"Honey, are you okay?"],[1789,1910,"How did you even find us?"],[1926,2274,"Well, let's just say I take good care of my manager."],[2566,2853,"Sweetheart, I bought two tickets for the observatory."],[2896,3234,"Next week, we're going to look at the stars together."],[3276,3363,"I love you, Dad."],[3513,3633,"You still owe us."],[3666,4000,"Fine. But first, you two"],[4000,4261,"are going to apologize to my daughter."],[4400,4630,"And then you will explain"],[4630,4829,"who told you to say those things."],[5093,5212,"You will all get to know"],[5212,5337,"who you're messing around with."]],"7":[[100,210,"Are you threatening me?"],[236,385,"Coming in so fancy."],[433,634,"I bet that's Emily's paid boyfriend."],[693,788,"Exactly."],[816,1003,"No wonder she got rid of the ex so quickly."],[1033,1151,"What a little hustler."],[1340,1527,"If you wanted to trick our kids,"],[1527,1706,"at least hire a decent actor."],[1733,1950,"Is this kid even old enough to drink?"],[2046,2233,"Are those limited edition?"],[2310,2353,"Pathetic."],[2369,2456,"Obviously fake."],[2473,2665,"Poor people can't even afford good knockoffs."],[2953,3070,"Our deals with Starry Globe"],[3070,3196,"Entertainment are canceled."],[3263,3390,"We're going bankrupt."],[3436,3593,"Who the hell did you piss off?"],[3746,3855,"Starry Globe pulled out."],[3896,4013,"Our stocks are plummeting."],[4050,4163,"Bank wants the margin now."],[4210,4341,"This is all your fault."],[4350,4466,"We're getting a divorce!"],[4593,4702,"Could this be you?"],[4763,4894,"Did you do all this?"],[5183,5333,"The entire school knows the truth."],[5376,5686,"You two kids apologize to Chloe immediately."],[5816,5996,"Principal, the kids were just messing around."],[6020,6218,"You're encouraging bullying?"],[6226,6317,"You're fired."],[6323,6616,"Get the hell out of here before I call security!"],[6900,7053,"We're sorry."],[7053,7116,"We gotta go."],[7140,7159,"Fuck."],[7196,7303,"You'll pay for this!"],[7543,7723,"We'll strengthen security."],[7766,7946,"Chloe will never be harmed again."],[7946,8133,"Otherwise, the entire board"],[8133,8358,"will be personally apologizing."],[8400,8712,"You better make sure that happens."],[8876,8923,"Come."],[9496,9840,"Maybe Chloe really does need a dad to protect her."],[9923,10083,"He seems so cold on the surface."],[10083,10267,"I didn't expect him of all people"],[10267,10406,"to step up for me when it mattered."],[10516,10620,"Um, thank you."],[10693,10773,"For today."],[10856,11116,"But in the future, please don't intervene."],[11133,11223,"You know how many rumors"],[11223,11383,"would fly if people found out."],[11826,12277,"Rumors, dating, or secretly married with a kid?"],[12403,12647,"Weren't you the one treating me like a kid?"],[12666,12812,"Are you scared to be caught up"],[12812,13099,"in a scandal with a kid?"],[13246,13486,"How can I prove you can rely on me, too?"],[13700,13849,"Lucas, it's really you!"]],"8":[[70,170,"Mom, it's Lucas!"],[170,304,"I'm your biggest fan!"],[304,433,"Can I please take a selfie with you?"],[433,509,"Of course you can."],[553,736,"But you need to tell your mom that"],[736,972,"she treats me a little better next time."],[1016,1204,"And she needs to pinky swear."],[1286,1521,"Mom, please, he was so cool today."],[1553,1672,"Chloe, put on your seatbelt first."],[1683,1877,"But Mom, please, just one selfie."],[1896,2081,"I'll skip ice cream for a whole month."],[2103,2226,"For a whole year."],[2353,2436,"I'm just joking."],[2866,2923,"Fine."],[2986,3043,"Yes!"],[3153,3246,"Smile!"],[3563,3783,"That's perfect. You should post it."],[3783,4047,"It makes us look like a real family."],[4076,4143,"Shut up!"],[4236,4416,"Hey, honey, put on your seatbelt. Let's go."],[5216,5333,"Hey, Lucas, someone from the"],[5333,5524,"entrance wanted you to have this personally."],[5860,6110,"Wow. Another obsessed fan?"],[6146,6265,"I'll check the stage positions."],[6376,6466,"Relax."],[8120,8231,"Please sit down."],[8273,8483,"Thank you so much for supporting me."],[8486,8720,"I'm very happy to see you all here."],[9086,9313,"If you dare look at the girl in red"],[9320,9633,"in the front row, I'll gouge her eyes out."],[10106,10183,"She's here?"],[10206,10276,"Lucas?"],[10373,10426,"Oh my God!"]],"9":[[0,163,"OH MY GOD!"],[163,273,"This is mortifying…"],[273,393,"How am I supposed to live with this?"],[906,1213,"Um... Sorry for that little hiccup."],[1593,1733,"Let's move on to the next segment."],[1773,2030,"The Q&A. Who's got a question?"],[2250,2516,"Alright, let's start with the next fan right here."],[3019,3303,"So smooth, even when she trips."],[3366,3553,"How can she be so cute?"],[3753,3890,"She saved me again."],[3945,4226,"Was it just because I'm her client or..."],[4226,4457,"does she like me just a little, too?"],[5096,5180,"Lucas!"],[5276,5443,"You better delete that meme right now!"],[6173,6256,"Oh, you bastard!"],[6426,6493,"Were you done?"],[6713,7066,"Wait, I... Who could this be?"]],"10":[[86,126,"I'm here!"],[143,296,"-Hey! What are you doing? -If you are cringing"],[296,526,"so much, there's no way I'm gonna delete it."],[566,660,"Delete it right now, you..."],[1676,1743,"Seduction tactic?"],[1913,2073,"Lucas, you're... hopeless."],[2143,2446,"Thanks. I know you went on stage to save me."],[2560,2630,"But I wanna know..."],[2733,3006,"Were you doing it out of professional instinct, or..."],[3086,3215,"to save the artist?"],[3215,3373,"Or because you see a kid in me?"],[3556,3650,"Or..."],[3703,3944,"Is there a tiniest chance"],[3944,4160,"it's because you have feelings for me?"],[4343,4581,"Does she want to kiss me, too?"],[5703,5743,"Oh!"],[5996,6092,"You actually have a little piece of glitter..."],[6179,6326,"And your eye almost fell in there."],[6463,6816,"I... just remembered there's something to do."],[7533,7582,"Can't believe he thought"],[7582,7720,"I was actually gonna kiss him."],[8303,8316,"Hello?"],[8340,8520,"Hey babe, I sent a blind date for you."],[8563,8743,"Right at night. Don't miss it."],[8743,8956,"A blind date? Um..."],[9229,9396,"Fatherless kids are wild!"],[9400,9654,"Fatherless children have no manners."],[9673,9729,"3 grand?"],[9796,9995,"Listen, you produced a liability"],[9995,10146,"and now you want me to pay?"],[10156,10223,"Dream on!"],[10336,10490,"Sure. Yeah, you know what?"],[10490,10586,"Maybe Chloe does need a dad."],[10750,10823,"Send me the address."],[10846,10951,"A blind date?"]],"11":[[779,836,"Hi, Emily."],[1096,1158,"I'm Toby."],[1309,1512,"It is an honor to meet you."],[1530,1619,"Lovely to meet you, too."],[2256,2573,"So, you're a talent manager, right?"],[2573,2622,"Yes."],[2636,2846,"You must work with a lot of celebrities."],[2910,2982,"It must be interesting."],[3123,3280,"Yeah, it's really fulfilling."],[3346,3432,"I love my job."],[3553,3635,"Do you like kids?"],[3651,3837,"Oh, yeah, of course."],[3853,4031,"I've actually always wanted a daughter."],[4110,4223,"She must be so adorable."],[4356,4469,"Chloe is a very sweet girl."],[4683,4876,"Would you excuse me? I need to wash my hands."],[4943,4983,"Of course."],[4983,5129,"Sorry, it's like a thing with me."],[5129,5246,"I'll be right back, I promise."],[5246,5301,"Yeah."],[5826,5993,"How can you talk to him so easily?"],[6116,6276,"You don't even know this man!"],[6333,6423,"I'm sorry."],[6426,6533,"Why are you even here?"],[6573,6670,"I am just your manager."],[6670,6886,"This is literally none of your business."],[6966,7022,"Fine."],[7123,7202,"I'm leaving."],[7429,7579,"Mama, don't worry."],[7579,7901,"She's almost 40 and she's in show business."],[7923,8034,"She makes a lot of money."],[8150,8323,"Yeah, my plan is I'm going to win her over"],[8323,8519,"and then the house will be in my name"],[8519,8733,"and after that, I'll dump her."],[9113,9163,"You again!"],[9233,9333,"What-What the..."]],"12":[[486,574,"What are you doing?"],[574,702,"What gives you the right to do that?"],[1176,1275,"You have a boyfriend?"],[1366,1492,"And you go on a blind date with me?"],[1569,1678,"What the fuck!"],[1730,1958,"I was just trying to snag your money, but surprise,"],[1958,2137,"apparently it already belongs to this guy."],[2336,2498,"So you were just here for a quick buck?"],[2566,2847,"What else? You're 40, divorced,"],[2886,3099,"dragging a kid around everywhere with you."],[3153,3275,"Do you think I actually cared?"],[3500,3721,"If you keep insulting her one more time,"],[3721,3898,"I'll make sure you will never be able"],[3898,4200,"to step a foot in LA again."],[4536,4623,"Wait a second, it's..."],[4710,4900,"Oh, no, no, no. It's you! I know..."],[5043,5376,"I may be almost 40, but I know a lot more about"],[5376,5529,"myself than I did when I was 20."],[5529,5770,"And I certainly don't have to put other people down"],[5770,5968,"to make myself feel superior."],[6770,7049,"Bitch! How dare you touch my man!"],[7053,7170,"You'll pay for this."]],"13":[[173,366,"Look, I..."],[446,753,"I'm so sorry I slapped you, okay? But..."],[876,943,"Would you at least let me"],[943,1137,"just put some ointment on it?"],[1386,1429,"Yeah."],[1576,1795,"But do you think this will"],[1795,1896,"make me forgive you?"],[1896,1979,"No chance."],[2276,2622,"I'm just saying that if you were photographed today,"],[2622,2798,"you would be on the front page tomorrow."],[3086,3106,"Hey."],[3126,3233,"Look, I don't care."],[3233,3496,"Didn't you learn from your last relationship?"],[3496,3626,"Not to rush in?"],[3710,3822,"It's for Chloe."],[3850,4015,"Okay, you saw what happened at school."],[4133,4295,"I can live without a husband."],[4295,4436,"But Chloe needs a father."],[4966,5303,"I mean, if you insist on finding someone for Chloe,"],[5353,5602,"the dating market is basically a mess right now."],[5664,5975,"Why don't you... consider me?"],[6150,6388,"Lucas, are you insane? You?"],[6443,6683,"I mean, I don't see the problem."],[6732,6873,"Chloe seems to like me."],[6903,7086,"Okay, but that's... that's totally different."],[7283,7396,"I may see a lot of problems."],[7564,7635,"Hey."]],"14":[[733,925,"Lucas! Get over here now!"],[980,1173,"There is a problem with the collab single."],[1423,1480,"It's okay."],[1559,1680,"Okay, you go to the meeting,"],[1680,1783,"I have to go to the office anyway."],[1823,1936,"We got a package from somebody"],[1936,2063,"and I have no idea what's in it."],[2153,2201,"Package?"],[2303,2376,"I'll come with you."],[2933,3026,"So weird."],[3313,3366,"I mean..."],[3723,3986,"Did you print the MV script for the collab?"],[4083,4270,"Fifteen copies for the meeting."],[4326,4421,"Fifteen copies?"],[4586,4756,"Who needs that many? You have to be kidding me."],[4939,5012,"Fine."],[5053,5131,"Fine."],[7206,7353,"Die, old hag!"],[7433,7688,"Touch him again and next time"],[7688,8119,"it won't just be a doll, it'll be you!"]],"15":[[1126,1256,"Check the security footage."],[1293,1493,"Did anyone suspicious enter or leave?"],[2203,2241,"Lucas!"],[2350,2584,"We've arranged you a publicity relationship"],[2584,2719,"to get you trending"],[2719,2860,"and to promote your collab."],[2919,3000,"A showmance?"],[3063,3346,"Before signing, we purely agreed to"],[3346,3604,"have only a musical collaboration."],[3633,3802,"The audience craves gossip."],[3805,3879,"A relationship will"],[3879,4019,"surely blow up the internet."],[4075,4335,"I work for music. Not crowd."],[4450,4553,"You're crossing a line!"],[4553,4850,"Clause 16 in the contract is crystal clear."],[4866,5011,"The client gets the final say."],[5060,5166,"Unless you're willing to pay an"],[5166,5400,"astronomical penalty for a contract breach."],[5460,5670,"This is our legal counsel, Ryan Grayson."],[5753,5972,"Yes, the contract does include this clause."],[5983,6157,"If Lucas refuses to comply,"],[6157,6377,"then it could indeed be considered a breach."],[6706,6872,"Lucas, what's wrong?"],[7013,7159,"Can't even act to save your own life?"],[7609,7733,"We're not agreeing to this."]],"16":[[196,256,"You?"],[283,442,"What happened to your company's security?"],[456,620,"Anybody could just walk in as they please?"],[629,903,"I'm Lucas' manager. Of course I can come in."],[959,1048,"You keep mentioning"],[1048,1213,"how the client gets the final say."],[1223,1423,"But you're conveniently skipping over the clause"],[1423,1689,"that states unless it potentially damages"],[1689,1885,"the actor's public image or reputation."],[2116,2286,"Manufacturing a fake relationship"],[2286,2516,"is already in breach of contract."],[2900,2973,"Nonsense!"],[2986,3193,"If we don't do the PR relationship,"],[3196,3329,"Anna won't sing."],[3337,3485,"Cancel the collaboration!"],[3686,3986,"I mean, sure. You could cancel."],[4046,4336,"Clause 7 specifically states the actor can terminate"],[4336,4753,"the contract if the client makes improper demands."],[4776,4910,"And you'll have to pay"],[4910,5096,"double the contract breach fee."],[5293,5395,"Who do you think you are?"],[5433,5574,"Go home and take care of your kid!"],[5689,5771,"She's correct."],[5853,6023,"As a lawyer, I must point out that"],[6046,6155,"the client's demand"],[6155,6340,"could indeed be a potential breach."],[6516,6590,"Ryan!"],[6673,6782,"Who do you work for?"],[6793,6983,"I work for the law. Not for you."],[8503,8746,"Just like before, no matter what happens,"],[8783,9027,"you always stand firmly by my side."],[9296,9533,"They... know each other?"]],"17":[[570,703,"I just returned from Boston."],[736,873,"It's been almost a year"],[873,994,"since we last saw each other, right?"],[1016,1094,"Yes."],[1113,1310,"I heard you're switching to international law."],[1363,1440,"That's exciting."],[1509,1576,"Thank you."],[1913,1993,"Smiling so happily?"],[2050,2132,"With him?"],[2163,2234,"No way."],[2273,2395,"I need to get her attention."],[2596,2656,"Hey, Ryan."],[2930,3086,"Thank you so much, Ryan, for earlier."],[3086,3154,"That was..."],[3186,3243,"No problem."],[3336,3404,"Great."],[3696,3797,"Lucas, what are you doing here?"],[3886,3945,"Stop..."],[4021,4213,"Well, I'm here to thank Ryan."],[4233,4293,"I mean..."],[4293,4533,"If it wasn't for him, I would've been in a fake"],[4533,4716,"romance with that woman, right?"],[4716,4846,"Where do you know each other from?"],[4926,4963,"We were..."],[5053,5186,"college classmates."],[5626,5833,"What a coincidence!"],[5834,5940,"It's so close."],[5996,6125,"Come on, smile!"],[6133,6380,"Huh? Ryan is here, too. Let's take a selfie."],[6479,6546,"Smile."],[6716,6883,"Lucas, how many missed calls is that?"],[6979,7056,"Why have you been declining"],[7056,7156,"somebody's calls lately?"]],"18":[[30,133,"That's just scammers."],[166,403,"They call me ten to a hundred times a day."],[506,563,"Lucas,"],[583,743,"I've listened to your work, too."],[776,863,"Very talented."],[863,986,"Obviously, thank you."],[1063,1326,"I mean, I don't understand law, so..."],[1336,1506,"I can't comment on you."],[1546,1613,"Good."],[1753,1896,"Let's just stick to our own lanes then."],[1980,2068,"Yes."],[2096,2320,"I mean, now I see why two are friends."],[2326,2524,"He's great with this word."],[2524,2585,"Lucas!"],[2680,2786,"Okay, I'll zip it up."],[2893,2952,"Carry on."],[3176,3266,"Let me send you home."],[3426,3602,"I mean, you are a very busy lawyer."],[3603,3713,"I can do that, too."],[4686,4739,"Okay, let's just..."],[5166,5231,"Rebecca?"],[5266,5423,"Well, I supposed to pick Chloe up from school."],[5443,5592,"Girl, you wanted a reliable dad"],[5592,5696,"for your daughter, right?"],[5696,5923,"A fortune teller told me your true love is a man"],[5923,6115,"with a black mole on his Adonis belt."],[6133,6269,"Check if someone around you has it."],[6269,6384,"That's crazy. How am I gonna go around"],[6384,6529,"looking for moles on guys' abs?"],[6529,6821,"I... I have to go. I... I'm at work."],[6934,7036,"It-"],[7216,7435,"I'm her knight in shining armor."],[7683,7726,"Let's go."],[7823,7898,"Lucas..."],[8696,8783,"Maybe you should come in"],[8783,8903,"for some water before you go?"],[8983,9043,"Please?"],[9051,9113,"Honey."],[9220,9429,"You know, Lucas has to go home and get some rest."],[9663,9748,"Your mom's right."],[9866,9960,"Got a show soon."],[10176,10263,"Have a good night."],[10270,10309,"You too."],[10386,10483,"-Bye. Thank you. -Good night."],[10633,10699,"Bye."],[11690,11765,"Hey, Luca-"],[11946,11986,"Come on."],[12029,12113,"Get down here tonight."],[12113,12276,"-Stop! Let go of me! -Get over here!"],[12293,12393,"-Come on. Let's go. -Stop!"],[12423,12473,"Come on."],[12500,12589,"-Come here! -Mom!"],[12746,12876,"What are you doing? I have sole custody."],[12885,12973,"Mom!"],[13126,13190,"Hey."],[13203,13264,"Oh, it's okay."],[13306,13433,"Who do you think you are?"],[13473,13582,"What do you want?"],[13636,13756,"Simple, convince Lucas to"],[13756,13903,"have a fake romance with Anna."],[13903,13983,"Oh, you're dreaming."],[14003,14106,"So I guess I'll start picking"],[14106,14240,"Chloe up from school every day."],[14540,14686,"You really think you can do that?"]],"19":[[370,526,"Oh, I see."],[573,807,"How does trash like you become a top star's agent?"],[836,936,"Turns out, she's just trying"],[936,1068,"to find Chloe a new daddy."],[1183,1286,"Even a top star"],[1346,1495,"wants my second-hand goods, huh?"],[1536,1891,"You know, some people, they don't deserve pearls."],[1989,2186,"They trample over them like a swine."],[2200,2377,"You just don't see Emily's worth."],[2489,2703,"If you touch them one more time,"],[2719,2846,"I'll make sure you'll be banished"],[2846,2973,"from the entertainment industry."],[3139,3313,"You cocky little brat."],[3329,3471,"You think you'll be on top forever?"],[3703,3823,"I won't be on top forever."],[3856,4042,"But at least I'll make sure"],[4042,4283,"that your career ends right now."],[6200,6273,"Hey."],[6300,6373,"Are you okay, little one?"],[6406,6608,"I don't want to go with him. I only want Mom."],[6733,6937,"As long as I'm here, no one will dare to hurt you."],[6986,7069,"I promise."],[7286,7383,"I appreciate it."],[7453,7618,"But you can't protect us forever."],[7883,7943,"I can."],[8113,8246,"Just marry me."],[8356,8478,"And I'll be Chloe's dad."],[8506,8709,"I can make sure I will always protect you."],[8923,9053,"Lucas, do you even know what you're saying?"],[9156,9176,"Yes."],[9363,9446,"I'm proposing to you."],[9446,9503,"Lucas..."],[9533,9576,"Right now."],[9626,9746,"I know it's a bad timing, but..."],[9806,9908,"I..."],[9983,10031,"Come on."],[10136,10263,"Lucas..."],[10263,10379,"This is crazy."],[10506,10673,"Okay, we all need to get home and get some rest."],[10956,11026,"Come here."]],"20":[[376,471,"He's crazy."],[676,765,"Am I crazy?"],[836,1167,"I mean, he's a superstar in his 20s."],[1300,1443,"He's every girl's dream man."],[1636,1975,"And he wants to marry me and be Chloe's stepdad?"],[2336,2507,"This has to be another one of his pranks."],[3516,3563,"Emily!"],[3736,3906,"Yeah, yeah, coming."],[5553,5832,"Oh my God, Emily, what did you just post?"],[5836,6043,"The whole internet is asking if he's a bottom."],[6060,6195,"People already made memes."],[7109,7183,"I'm done for."],[7203,7350,"I am so dead."],[7666,7865,"Whoever did this is dead meat!"],[8883,9006,"Lucas, I... It was a typo!"],[9006,9057,"It was a typo."],[9073,9143,"I didn't mean to."],[9203,9270,"A typo?"],[9286,9342,"Yeah."],[9433,9561,"So it was you."],[9746,9897,"You called me Super Sissy."],[9897,10075,"No, I didn't mean it like that."],[10116,10208,"All right then."],[10596,10868,"Let me show you whether I'm a sissy"],[10933,11009,"or not."],[11173,11230,"Are you crazy?"],[11253,11382,"This is the office..."],[11545,11613,"I..."]],"21":[[3,206,"A fortune teller told me your true love is a man"],[206,400,"with a black mole on his Adonis belt."],[433,629,"Check if someone around you has it."],[746,811,"That mole."],[846,993,"Could he really be my soulmate?"],[1053,1136,"No?"],[1216,1266,"No."],[1266,1436,"Why am I even daydreaming right now?"],[1789,1833,"I..."],[1833,1933,"I will handle it."],[2033,2310,"What about the emotional damage?"],[2353,2640,"How are you going to compensate me?"],[2769,2853,"Um..."],[2876,2906,"Just..."],[3019,3123,"Just tell me."],[3226,3363,"Okay, whatever you want, I'll make it happen."],[3736,3822,"Except that..."],[3896,4090,"There is no way I'm making you Chloe's dad."],[4376,4439,"Anything"],[4500,4578,"but that?"],[4766,4843,"Don't be silly."],[6353,6563,"You really think I'm going to kiss you?"],[6602,6689,"What? I..."],[6923,6993,"I mean..."],[7033,7204,"Because you are so sincere,"],[7204,7333,"I'm going to give you a chance."],[7376,7505,"My water heater is broken."],[7546,7633,"Come and fix it"],[7656,7733,"tonight."],[7826,7883,"But-"],[7906,7983,"Oh!"],[8006,8180,"And please bring Chloe."],[8180,8375,"You can stop me from being her father, but..."],[8396,8656,"You can't stop her from liking me."],[9003,9094,"Hey, hold on."],[9106,9357,"See you tonight. Ciao!"],[10323,10626,"Lukiepoo, don't you remember me?"],[10626,10793,"Why did you let her touch you?"],[10793,10914,"You belong to me!"],[10923,11200,"If you keep seeing her, I'll kill her!"],[11209,11276,"Psycho!"],[11416,11465,"Ah!"]],"22":[[23,83,"Psycho!"],[263,326,"Ah!"],[336,548,"Damn, I just wanted to trick her into coming out."],[548,653,"It's actually broken."],[1176,1367,"Yeah, come in! It's not locked."],[1706,1906,"Don't just stand there. Come over, come help me."],[2166,2216,"Oh my god!"],[2233,2438,"Be... Be careful! It's hot..."],[2523,2651,"What are you two doing?"],[2667,2775,"Um..."],[3123,3258,"I think we should go."],[3360,3465,"You!"],[3465,3675,"You stay here until this is fixed."],[3716,3800,"Because you owe me one."],[3853,3966,"The super sissy headline."],[4096,4178,"You're impossible."],[4193,4359,"Mom, are we gonna stay here?"],[4359,4482,"It's so pretty!"],[4500,4712,"See? Even Chloe likes it here."],[4856,4996,"Your song's gone viral."],[5026,5192,"I've seen so much news about you online."],[5203,5306,"Is it fun being a singer?"],[5346,5420,"Yeah, it is."],[5443,5674,"Look, this is the new demo."],[5674,5772,"I'll show you that."],[6706,6756,"Maybe..."],[6943,7173,"maybe Lucas could actually be a good dad."],[7359,7506,"This is crazy."],[7586,7656,"How did he rope me"],[7656,7766,"into his train of thought?"]],"23":[[16,243,"Chloe, hey, it's time to go to bed, sweetie."],[426,553,"I'll listen to it tomorrow, okay?"],[559,618,"Yeah."],[640,835,"Just take my bedroom upstairs."],[866,943,"I'll sleep on the couch."],[980,1093,"It's too late to drive home."],[1166,1213,"Sure."],[1926,2158,"No. Before I resolve this,"],[2216,2404,"I need to make sure they are safe."],[3556,3683,"Mom, let's go to lunch together."],[3746,3846,"Chloe, you're back already?"],[3946,4053,"Shouldn't you be in school?"],[4120,4270,"It's school anniversary today."],[4323,4430,"Half day off."],[4430,4540,"Come on, hop in."],[4540,4621,"It's lunchtime."],[4700,4886,"And as for the big-shot lawyer over there,"],[4936,5086,"I think he shouldn't intrude"],[5086,5250,"on a little family lunch, right?"],[5250,5496,"Young people are always changeable."],[5689,5837,"Don't come to my place with Chloe"],[5837,5928,"the next couple weeks."],[5976,6074,"I'm a bit busy."],[6226,6360,"I should have expected this."],[6529,6825,"How could a top idol fall for a 40-year-old like me?"],[7083,7409,"Uncle Ryan, long time no see. I missed you so much."],[7443,7546,"I missed you, too, Chloe."],[7613,7754,"Mom, why don't we"],[7754,8043,"bring Uncle Ryan along, too? Please?"],[8476,8536,"Of course."],[8556,8706,"Yes! Yes, yes, yes!"],[8813,8934,"Thank you for the invitation."],[9103,9259,"-You can sit next to me. -Yes."],[10246,10386,"I would like to have the chili."],[10426,10543,"Emily, what about you?"],[10556,10790,"I heard the Cajun crawfish boil"],[10790,10916,"is actually excellent here."],[10973,11063,"Would you like to try?"],[11133,11208,"Lucas, I actually..."],[11208,11373,"Emily doesn't like spicy food."],[11666,11989,"How about the PB&J bagel bites?"],[12003,12150,"Emily's allergic to peanuts."],[12493,12863,"How about the seafood platter?"],[12976,13096,"Emily doesn't like crab."]],"24":[[106,370,"I guess I'll just order for myself."],[429,660,"Give you the honor to order for the table."],[953,993,"Thank you."],[1059,1136,"You're welcome."],[1835,1977,"Good choice, Ryan."],[1983,2061,"Thank you."],[2269,2536,"These are all the things that Emily likes."],[2733,3095,"Wow, you are so good with people."],[3139,3296,"There's so much I can learn from him."],[3413,3634,"Uncle Ryan, I haven't seen you in a long time."],[3653,3903,"Did you come this time just to see Mom?"],[3983,4083,"-Chloe... -Honestly..."],[4103,4339,"I did want to see her, but I also missed you, Chloe."],[4623,4857,"That sounds like you don't work a lot."],[4903,4994,"You work a lot?"],[5276,5336,"It's okay."],[5386,5666,"My schedule is pretty flexible, unlike a top star."],[5773,5973,"If Chloe ever needs anything,"],[5973,6081,"she can always come to me."],[6463,6553,"Is that so?"],[6636,6878,"I've never seen you around when Chloe was in trouble."],[6979,7257,"Maybe, because unlike a certain someone,"],[7290,7505,"I respect Emily's personal boundaries"],[7505,7803,"and I wouldn't just show up somewhere uninvited."],[7946,8100,"-Enjoy yourself. -Thank you."],[8326,8548,"Oh, my. It's Lucas!"],[9032,9093,"Hey."],[10014,10283,"Lucas, what has gotten into you?"],[10443,10784,"I'm sorry. I've mistaken her with someone."],[11040,11202,"Why did he react so strongly?"]],"25":[[453,696,"Mom, if you had to choose between Uncle Ryan and"],[696,823,"Uncle Lucas, who would you pick?"],[1123,1303,"Well, if it's about choosing a dad,"],[1303,1563,"I choose Uncle Lucas. He's a superstar."],[1603,1860,"Honey, don't say that."],[1963,2019,"Lucas and I..."],[2239,2615,"First of all, I am 11 years older than him,"],[2615,2823,"and second of all, he's..."],[2986,3101,"a top star."],[3126,3183,"Okay, he and I..."],[3183,3300,"Yeah, but just now,"],[3346,3563,"I only mentioned Lucas once,"],[3576,3796,"yet you talked so much about him."],[3823,4121,"Looks like your heart already has the answer."],[4147,4273,"Mm-hmm?"],[4353,4495,"Well, it's gonna late. Goodnight."],[4566,4636,"Love you, Mom."],[4663,4737,"Love you."],[6796,7026,"Let's hang out together some other time."],[7056,7146,"Just the two of us."],[7356,7644,"Looks like your heart already has the answer."],[8313,8507,"Goodnight. See you tomorrow."],[9690,9934,"Okay, and action."],[10343,10475,"I forgot my lines."],[10500,10550,"Cuts."],[10584,10658,"Cuts."],[10876,10976,"You're gonna do something."],[11066,11133,"Yeah... Um..."],[11133,11311,"All right, let's try again. Let's try again, please."],[11479,11620,"Here we go. Slate in, thank you."],[11800,11995,"And action!"],[12293,12633,"Oh, I'm sorry. I'm too nervous."],[12736,12927,"Okay, one more, please. Let's go again."],[13119,13256,"The lines are too tricky."],[13280,13364,"-Cut. -I'm sorry."],[13373,13446,"I'm sorry."],[13453,13558,"I'm sorry..."],[13563,13727,"Okay, one more, please."],[13926,14085,"I'm sorry. I..."],[14085,14206,"I keep forgetting my lines."],[14206,14474,"You know what? You're not impressing anyone, okay?"],[14486,14703,"You are wasting everyone's time."],[14736,14835,"Can we get someone else?"],[15256,15336,"I..."],[15336,15490,"Let's take five, please. Let's take five."],[16390,16638,"You know, Emily, jealousy doesn't really suit you."]],"26":[[30,313,"You know, Emily, jealousy doesn't really suit you."],[473,539,"No."],[640,693,"Not at all."],[1016,1153,"I heard you kidding, still saying no?"],[1226,1371,"I mean, I clearly saw you"],[1371,1526,"glancing at Sophie the whole time."],[1669,1819,"Because I was checking the time."],[1863,1953,"I mean, she did four takes."],[1953,2083,"We can't afford to waste this budget."],[2123,2315,"Oh yeah, I didn't even notice."],[2503,2676,"Hey, why are you so anxious?"],[2776,3060,"Um, you know what, I'm gonna get you"],[3060,3241,"more throat lozenges."],[3453,3518,"Stupid."],[3846,3950,"So what's going on? Can we go or..."],[3953,4199,"I'm sorry, it's all gonna work out, I promise."],[4213,4424,"I'm gonna get through this. It's gonna be quick."],[4424,4496,"Mm-hmm."],[4496,4638,"I just need a little longer, okay?"],[4638,4730,"-Okay. -I'm sorry."],[4870,4947,"What's wrong? What happened?"],[5100,5339,"Sophie disappeared. Her phone is off."],[5366,5513,"There's no sign of her anywhere."],[5618,5706,"Um..."],[5770,5841,"Did you find her?"],[5933,6155,"Come on, we need to shoot immediately."],[6900,7002,"What are you looking at me for?"],[7096,7260,"You. Come here."]],"27":[[30,311,"No, no, no, no. I have never acted in an ad before."],[350,526,"Yeah, you were an acting teacher before."],[563,770,"A 30-second ad? Easy. You should do that."],[823,1001,"How... how did you know that?"],[1076,1223,"A nod from Lucas is rare."],[1226,1382,"You should not miss this chance."],[1706,1746,"Fine."],[2026,2083,"Happy?"],[2143,2283,"Oh, let's see."],[2469,2580,"He's brilliant."],[2616,2750,"Okay. So, when she gets back..."],[5326,5396,"Oh my God."],[5476,5669,"Breathtaking! Perfect."],[5686,5813,"Let's roll, please. Let's roll."],[5920,5986,"Don't be afraid."],[6033,6095,"Just think about"],[6095,6242,"it's just you and me."],[6330,6393,"Right here."],[6543,6603,"You and me."],[6656,6804,"And... action!"],[7246,7331,"Yes!"],[7500,7636,"Cut! We got it!"],[8100,8293,"I'm sorry. It's just been so long."],[8323,8440,"No, you did it."],[8440,8593,"You did it. Amazing."],[8600,8746,"You shouldn't doubt yourself."],[8786,9009,"You shine brighter than anyone else in this room."],[9009,9163,"And you're not meant to be in the shadows."],[9283,9333,"Lucas."],[9340,9676,"You are meant to be in the center of the stage."],[9716,9800,"That's where you belong."]],"28":[[396,581,"Lucas is more mature than I imagined."],[700,871,"He can even guide me into character."],[1090,1361,"Emily? Lucas wants you to bring the outfit over."],[1480,1583,"Oh, okay, yes."],[1833,1918,"We found Sophie."],[2039,2142,"She said she wanted to smoke,"],[2142,2240,"but someone knocked her out"],[2240,2343,"and locked her in a car."],[2446,2659,"Lucas, you need to watch out."],[2733,2884,"It's the crazy fan again."],[3000,3048,"Hey."],[3339,3403,"What's going on?"],[3486,3543,"Listen."],[3593,3780,"From now on, you and Chloe..."],[3780,3885,"don't leave the house."],[3885,3961,"You stay home."],[3961,4124,"You don't leave my sight."],[4163,4265,"Why? What happened?"],[4303,4528,"Don't worry about it. It's for your own good."],[4656,4743,"For my own good?"],[4823,4939,"Yeah, Mark always used to say that."],[5003,5365,"And then, he went bankrupt without telling me."],[5386,5570,"Then he got a promotion without telling me."],[5570,5728,"And then he jumped into some other woman's bed"],[5728,5926,"without telling me all for my own good."],[5926,6002,"Emily!"],[6116,6206,"Just trust me."],[6289,6490,"I won't hurt you and I won't lie to you."],[6513,6676,"Just do as I say."],[6715,6801,"Please."],[6929,7216,"I'm here to work for you. Not here to be your slave."],[9426,9516,"Been busy lately?"],[9596,9743,"I'd like to take you out for dinner."],[9970,10238,"Yeah. Of course."],[10238,10344,"I have time."],[10392,10510,"Send me the address."]],"29":[[603,689,"Okay,"],[689,1069,"Lucas has an interview day after tomorrow."],[1083,1293,"I'm going to put that in his contract and..."],[1433,1526,"It's for your own good."],[1573,1713,"Just do as I say."],[1756,1883,"I'm here to work for you."],[1916,2024,"Not here to be your slave."],[2323,2387,"Forget it."],[2546,2702,"We'll do that when I get home."],[3161,3244,"Oh!"],[3460,3586,"I heard you shot as a stand-in"],[3586,3726,"in the commercial yesterday."],[3923,4036,"That's really none of your business."],[4323,4597,"Single moms should stay home with their kids."],[4616,4809,"40s still chasing stardom."],[5303,5363,"You know what?"],[5573,5626,"You're right."],[6820,7105,"David, I will go on that reality show"],[7140,7226,"you mentioned last time"],[7323,7436,"under one condition."],[8131,8255,"Looking for me?"],[8255,8405,"It's a little crowded in here."],[8409,8509,"Let's go to my car."],[8536,8628,"No need for that."],[8633,8776,"I already wanted to let you know"],[8776,9033,"that we will terminate all your projects."],[9100,9165,"What?"],[9179,9323,"I have three albums left."],[9323,9411,"You can't do that."],[9453,9524,"I can."],[9533,9659,"I'm the ace of the company,"],[9696,9831,"and I don't want to see you here."],[9866,10093,"And I won't just terminate your contract."],[10093,10317,"I will actually blacklist you from all platforms."],[10536,10607,"You..."],[10640,10739,"for Emily?"],[10766,10943,"You're gonna destroy my career?"],[10976,11318,"The newbie, Emily, actually managed to win"],[11326,11565,"three rookie awards in the second year."],[11636,11690,"And you?"],[11706,12056,"You sing off-key and sleep with producers for roles."],[12173,12343,"How dare you question her?"],[16176,16431,"Perhaps Lucas had his reasons before,"],[16500,16613,"but Chloe probably needs a"],[16613,16793,"steady and mature father figure"],[16793,16967,"like Ryan, who can guide her more."],[17439,17497,"Shit."]],"30":[[260,363,"Are you free tonight?"],[413,596,"I need to review tomorrow's interview."],[759,863,"Chloe's school is having a"],[863,1090,"father-daughter camping trip next week, right?"],[1090,1157,"Mm."],[1216,1363,"I think she should go with a father."],[1963,2033,"You okay?"],[2363,2596,"I... Um..."],[2753,2948,"Emily, Lucas blacklisted Anna."],[2948,3214,"What? Why would Lucas do that?"],[3306,3629,"I really need to talk to you about something."],[4043,4163,"I'm sorry. We're gonna have to"],[4163,4256,"talk about this another day."],[4256,4426,"I... I have to go."],[4556,4623,"So sorry."],[4633,4705,"I'm sorry."],[5050,5216,"For the father-daughter camping trip,"],[5356,5490,"I could be Chloe's dad, too."],[6286,6417,"Why did you blacklist Anna?"],[6583,6736,"Sorry for my stupid words earlier."],[6956,7140,"But I couldn't bear to see you suffer."],[7193,7283,"And I couldn't"],[7376,7552,"and wouldn't want to"],[7620,7811,"have you listen to those terrible things."],[8223,8424,"And I don't want you to be just my co-worker."]],"31":[[3103,3206,"I feel like I'm dreaming."],[3433,3483,"Me too."],[3570,3686,"If you're just chasing a thrill,"],[3686,3779,"I can leave right now."],[3813,3923,"Do you think a thrill..."],[4020,4146,"last eight years?"],[4343,4427,"Eight years?"],[4550,4712,"Yeah. Eight years."],[4843,5100,"Remember when I was 17, when those..."],[5250,5389,"guys in the rehearsal room"],[5389,5536,"were mocking me for the accent?"],[5586,5724,"You came down and stepped in."],[5763,6017,"And you said, the audience..."],[6239,6326,"The audience always"],[6326,6536,"remembers the person that works hard."],[6653,6746,"Remember that?"],[6893,7059,"That was you? You never told me that."],[7103,7176,"Eight years ago."],[7316,7609,"I wanted to be worthy of you before telling you."],[7916,7997,"Do you feel my heart?"],[8083,8308,"It's beating faster than being on stage."],[8563,8619,"Let's go."],[8696,8889,"I want to give you an unforgettable date."],[9036,9097,"Let's go."],[9496,9721,"So, do you want salted caramel or vanilla?"],[9770,9959,"Doesn't matter. I'm not eating anything."],[10170,10320,"Okay, I'll have..."],[10476,10523,"Thank you."],[10826,10949,"So, are you going to wear that"],[10949,11039,"wherever you go, or..."],[11216,11276,"Do you want some?"],[11413,11508,"Lucas."],[11676,11935,"Oh my gosh, it's Lucas! Let's go see!"],[12000,12223,"Oh my god, it's truly Lucas!"],[12276,12438,"Lucas! Lucas!"],[12540,12630,"In here! In here!"]],"32":[[633,741,"Hey, hey, Lucas!"],[1046,1100,"What are you doing?"],[1100,1240,"Come on. Catch your breath or something."],[1313,1437,"Get in, get in, get in!"],[1850,1939,"What is going on? Why is it that-"],[2090,2192,"Shh."],[2393,2558,"I swear I saw Lucas."],[2583,2761,"How did he disappear around the corner?"],[3613,3846,"I saw him with a woman."],[3939,4203,"Once I find them, I'll destroy her."],[4253,4504,"He belongs to me, alone!"],[4883,5071,"Lucas, what is going on? You're scaring me."],[5086,5293,"So, there's this woman, and"],[5293,5464,"she sends me strange messages."],[5503,5677,"Then calls, then emails."],[5713,5890,"Okay. And then?"],[5943,6159,"And then things to my villa."],[6193,6366,"Letters with blood in it."],[6389,6644,"And then also photos of us."],[6750,6878,"And latest a doll"],[6886,7133,"with a wristband of my concert around its neck."],[7190,7312,"Lucas, did you call the police?"],[7403,7616,"Yes. But all the messages are from"],[7616,7782,"virtual emails from different IPs."],[7843,7992,"I recognize the voice just now."],[8090,8306,"That's why you don't want Chloe going to your house."],[8379,8596,"Is this why you insisted that I stay in your sight?"],[8703,8753,"Yeah."],[9009,9068,"Lucas."],[9286,9526,"Being silly. Okay? I'm here."],[9646,10001,"No matter how crazy she is, she's just one person."],[10043,10284,"She can't win. Okay?"],[11063,11291,"Lucas. You did all this?"]],"33":[[70,296,"Yes, an unforgettable date."],[353,536,"As promised, ma'am."],[3571,3698,"Oh, so great."],[3821,3960,"Good idea with a van, huh?"],[4556,4596,"What's up?"],[4626,4686,"My phone."],[5009,5099,"Hello?"],[5221,5306,"What?"],[5367,5496,"Chloe's in the hospital."],[5593,5763,"I'm coming right now. Yeah, I know."],[5786,5843,"Which hospital?"],[5926,6020,"You can't come, okay?"],[6020,6126,"It's really crowded"],[6126,6206,"and you might get photographed."],[6206,6303,"I have to go."],[6436,6553,"I'm gonna get there, okay?"],[6623,6683,"I'm sorry."],[7326,7486,"What the heck with that crazy fan?"],[8266,8306,"Hey."],[8566,8656,"Mama's here, baby."],[8726,8867,"Rebecca had to leave."],[8867,9053,"I knew you didn't arrive, so she called me."],[9090,9181,"But don't worry."],[9263,9396,"Chloe's fever has already gone down."],[9529,9606,"Thank you."],[9659,9812,"Hey, you look exhausted."],[9826,10020,"Listen, it's okay to lean on me."],[10240,10576,"They look so right together."],[10729,10923,"I can't even be beside her in public."]],"34":[[183,350,"What kind of mother are you?"],[423,585,"Kid has a hundred three degree fever"],[585,711,"and you didn't even notice?"],[1046,1156,"Okay, stop."],[1786,1963,"Would you stop yelling in the hospital?"],[1973,2073,"You're scaring Chloe."],[2096,2355,"You spent all day orbiting celebrities."],[2396,2585,"You didn't even notice that your daughter is sick?"],[2586,2709,"You're not fit to be a mother!"],[2726,2948,"You cheated on me during our marriage,"],[2956,3076,"and you neglected Chloe."],[3076,3184,"Who are you to say that?"],[3383,3621,"Sir, don't yell in the hallway."],[3656,3698,"Ha."],[3750,3854,"Who's this hero?"],[3903,4041,"Saving the damsel in distress?"],[4066,4185,"Who is that Lucas character?"],[4300,4497,"We should focus on the child first,"],[4497,4596,"not blaming each other."],[4623,4746,"Focus on the child?"],[4778,4932,"More like focus on whoring."],[5000,5136,"Mark, save it."],[5140,5263,"If I were you,"],[5263,5336,"I would worry about the"],[5336,5547,"horns on your own head first."],[5636,5706,"What do you mean?"],[5873,6120,"Why don't you go ask your true love?"],[7683,7842,"Just a passer-by."],[7852,8030,"You have such a punchable face."]],"35":[[200,275,"What?"],[2200,2284,"Hey."],[2486,2706,"I was just putting her to bed."],[2706,2820,"I'm about to leave."],[2996,3090,"So do you got what you wanted"],[3090,3216,"and you don't want to see me anymore?"],[3396,3496,"That's not what I meant."],[3570,3812,"Today after the kiss, I lost control."],[3812,4071,"I shouldn't have confessed impulsively."],[4123,4271,"I put you both in danger."],[4339,4523,"You promised to face everything together."],[4573,4645,"Remember?"],[5650,5833,"I will keep you both safe."],[5986,6058,"I promise."],[6645,6746,"Recovery's going well."],[6746,6831,"It's nice to see that"],[6831,6982,"she's progressing more than we had hoped."],[7009,7228,"Honestly, I hope it's really impactful."],[7400,7500,"Chloe's still weak."],[7500,7667,"It's best if you spend more time"],[7667,7859,"with her. Help her with some exercises."],[7883,7992,"-What kind of exercises? -What kind of exercises?"],[8143,8179,"Uh..."],[8179,8331,"Do you mind just sending it to my email?"],[8400,8456,"Of course."],[8963,9243,"I'm not too busy this second half of the year..."],[9290,9485,"I can spend time with Chloe regularly."],[10146,10451,"And I can be a consistent presence"],[10470,10693,"in Chloe's life and in yours."],[10776,11006,"Mom? Are you with Lucas now?"]],"36":[[83,289,"Mom? Are you with Lucas now?"],[379,663,"Um... Hi. Hi, honey, I..."],[663,706,"Thank you."],[909,1132,"-I... -Yes. We are dating."],[1213,1413,"Yes! Lucas is gonna be my dad now!"],[2123,2192,"Hello?"],[2234,2326,"The Weber-Hopp Musical?"],[2386,2496,"And you want Lucas for it?"],[3446,3603,"Lucas, are you sure you're not"],[3603,3726,"interested in the Weber-Hopp Musical?"],[3793,4060,"No time. I plan to rest and to"],[4060,4201,"take you and Chloe traveling."],[4366,4443,"I don't think you understand."],[4443,4597,"It's an incredible opportunity."],[4943,5016,"Lucas!"],[5163,5215,"Boss?"],[5330,5406,"Shit."],[7313,7400,"Do you know how crazy"],[7400,7538,"people went fighting for the script?"],[7563,7720,"And you disappeared with your phone off?"],[7776,8040,"Weber-Hopp specifically requested you."],[8083,8178,"Why not sign?"],[8306,8646,"I, um... have to take care of my daughter."],[8666,8792,"I plan to take a rest."],[8836,8925,"Your daughter."],[8925,9076,"Since when... since when did you..."]],"37":[[16,156,"Daughter? Since when did you..."],[176,383,"Look, I don't care who you're with."],[400,475,"But this"],[475,667,"is a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity."],[693,954,"Miss this musical, you'll never get another chance!"],[983,1187,"Then let it go."],[1187,1521,"I don't work for just one opportunity."],[2219,2279,"Oh."],[3576,3753,"You really think you have a steady career?"],[3800,3878,"Producers are already"],[3878,4029,"asking me for a backup male lead."],[4089,4201,"One more chance."],[4350,4446,"Will you sign?"],[4696,4750,"No."],[4913,5101,"Fine. You stubborn ass."],[5150,5298,"I'll prepare the PR myself."],[5410,5728,"Thanks. And take care on the way."],[6566,6656,"Oh my god."],[6679,6756,"Whoo..."],[7010,7124,"So..."],[7177,7325,"That wasn't enough."],[7325,7430,"Do you want to pay me?"],[7736,7899,"Chloe doesn't need you fawning over her."],[7933,8115,"Okay, you should've listened to David"],[8115,8229,"and signed the contract."],[8276,8473,"Look, kids grow up so fast."],[8473,8688,"If I don't spend time with her right now,"],[8696,8896,"she might not accept me as a father later."],[8909,9199,"Lucas, I am Chloe's mother."],[9199,9319,"I will take care of her."],[9393,9584,"You... You should..."],[9600,9656,"Enough!"],[9776,9913,"I don't even like the script."],[9980,10112,"Perhaps stepping back"],[10112,10356,"from the spotlight and obsessive fans"],[10381,10586,"is the only way to keep you safe."]],"38":[[876,943,"Annoying guy."],[1656,1763,"Ryan?"],[1789,1936,"Now's not really a good time. Um..."],[1966,2083,"Can we meet one last time?"],[2353,2459,"Do you have to see him?"],[2526,2676,"Or rather stay with me?"],[3576,3776,"Lukiepoo, where did you go?"],[3792,4073,"I haven't seen you for three days."],[4073,4338,"Is that old hag hiding you?"],[4786,4883,"What's up, bro? How you been?"],[4900,5046,"I haven't seen you in a minute."],[5136,5186,"Alright."],[5216,5328,"What's up? What's new?"],[5426,5489,"Hey, Emily!"],[5686,5761,"Come over here."],[6020,6328,"Everyone, this is my girlfriend, Emily Carter."],[6526,6604,"Girlfriend?"],[6743,6972,"Are you sure she's not your aunt?"],[7293,7612,"He once said he loved a girl for eight years."],[7666,7739,"Is that her?"]],"39":[[0,103,"Bro, are you serious?"],[143,264,"You always joked about liking someone"],[264,368,"ten years old than you."],[393,446,"It's real?"],[446,576,"I've been telling you for years."],[656,813,"Yes, I'm serious."],[883,1066,"Bro, are you out of your mind?"],[1066,1261,"I thought our friend Maya has so much more..."],[1268,1338,"What?"],[1411,1604,"Do you think I need your approval for anything?"],[1626,1691,"I've been telling you,"],[1691,1832,"I've been looking for the woman I love,"],[1832,1919,"and it's Emily."],[2016,2159,"If you can't accept that,"],[2159,2310,"we can't be any friends anymore."],[2380,2467,"Down?"],[2477,2587,"Get them out of here."],[4126,4353,"What are you still thinking about?"],[4426,4486,"I..."],[4710,4753,"I?"],[4896,5126,"What they said isn't entirely wrong."],[5146,5457,"I mean, maybe our age difference"],[5457,5587,"and our experience..."],[5587,5663,"Stop!"]],"40":[[23,53,"Age?"],[133,173,"Yes."],[256,482,"Come on, I was born when you were in school."],[533,753,"And it's so cool that I can step up"],[753,1065,"as a cool dad for Chloe, it is."],[1496,1571,"I just..."],[1669,1769,"I just want to be sure"],[1769,1903,"that you're not going to regret this later."],[1946,1997,"Listen."],[2063,2385,"What I'd regret is not pursuing you sooner."],[2493,2678,"Should I swear on something or..."],[2713,2761,"No."],[2873,2966,"I believe you."],[2983,3023,"Okay."],[3366,3445,"Got you."],[3500,3755,"I finally got you, darling."],[4793,4886,"Send me the original."],[4923,5016,"The money is on the way"],[5016,5246,"Lucas, you forced me to do this."],[5246,5589,"You should be kept at my home for my eyes only."],[5589,5674,"What do you mean?"],[6106,6261,"Got you at last."],[6306,6433,"Lucas, I can't believe you made"],[6433,6663,"the entire industry blacklist me."],[6740,6835,"I'll make you pay."]],"41":[[590,782,"Lucas is in a secret relationship."],[813,1053,"If we leak this, his fans will turn on him."],[1343,1463,"Can you explain this?"],[1673,1893,"Uh... It's showbiz."],[1896,2037,"How dare you lie to me?"],[2060,2161,"You little slut!"],[2346,2436,"If it weren't for me,"],[2436,2590,"you wouldn't be in this position."],[2630,2803,"You're just a blacklisted loser now."],[2826,2903,"We're done!"],[3213,3474,"Lucas, Emily, you did this."],[3536,3686,"I'll ruin you."],[4716,4774,"Hello?"],[4816,5029,"Babe, check the trending news."],[5043,5196,"You and Lucas were exposed."],[5236,5372,"It's the photos of you kissing Lucas."],[5372,5463,"What? I..."],[5806,5870,"Oh my God."],[5923,6033,"No, no, no, no, no."],[6116,6193,"This is not good."],[6293,6355,"Impossible."],[6436,6605,"Lucas doesn't have that bad of taste."],[6605,6802,"She's old enough to be his mom!"],[6841,7063,"Old hag, let Lucas go!"],[7063,7236,"Outsiders think it's cute,"],[7275,7477,"but to us true fans,"],[7545,7728,"the world's ending."]],"42":[[0,76,"-Whoa! Whoa! -Sir!"],[76,280,"Sir! Is Lucas really in a relationship?"],[296,424,"We heard he's dating his manager."],[424,573,"Are there any conflicts of interest there?"],[573,722,"The old witch must go!"],[787,905,"Lucas, come out!"],[905,1089,"We're waiting for you to debunk the rumors!"],[1116,1336,"Listen! There was a misunderstanding!"],[1353,1440,"Everyone calm down!"],[1440,1578,"The official statement's coming soon!"],[1578,1653,"Coming soon?"],[1663,1704,"Soon!"],[1713,1865,"Ten minutes or ten hours?"],[1883,1989,"We can wait. Can the fan?"],[1989,2110,"We need an answer now!"],[2110,2277,"Not one second longer!"],[2711,2792,"This way."],[2792,2918,"Mr. Lucas' instructions."],[2993,3061,"Thanks."],[3643,3736,"Explain this!"],[4056,4183,"I'm not against you dating."],[4183,4279,"But hide it better!"],[4300,4490,"Now, how do I explain this to the brands?"],[4753,4845,"Perfect."],[4845,5056,"Saves us paying paparazzi to sneak photos."],[5126,5284,"And it saves us money."],[5473,5568,"Public?"],[5677,5782,"Are you willing to"],[5782,5984,"ruin your career for a woman?"],[6116,6547,"Compared to my career, Emily means more to me."],[10253,10363,"-Please! -Can you tell us anything else?"],[10363,10476,"-We have no other information."],[10523,10673,"And there's nothing else I can tell you."],[10776,10886,"Oh, Lucas!"],[11029,11158,"Can you answer a few questions?"],[11166,11305,"Please, people need to know!"]],"43":[[622,719,"It's Lucas!"],[719,856,"Please answer the fans!"],[856,944,"Lucas!"],[1136,1273,"This is my girlfriend"],[1356,1493,"and I love her with my whole heart."],[1756,1865,"Everything is said."],[1873,1988,"If you keep harassing her,"],[1988,2126,"I'm gonna come after you with my lawyers."],[2173,2229,"Let's go."],[2283,2326,"Okay."],[2403,2498,"-Lucas. Wait!"],[2498,2659,"Are you married? Are you engaged?"],[2659,2750,"Are you pregnant?"],[2986,3064,"Madness."],[3200,3351,"All of them are mad!"],[3639,3757,"You were too impulsive."],[3796,3907,"Your fans..."],[3966,4042,"ads, everything..."],[4042,4152,"It could take a big hit."],[4266,4336,"So be it."],[4413,4740,"As long as my singing isn't affected, it's fine."],[4786,4956,"What if work stops coming to you?"],[5176,5336,"Then I will sing on the streets."],[5353,5523,"Okay, stop joking. I'm serious."],[5536,5628,"I'm serious."],[5689,5863,"Even if I have to give up my career,"],[5863,5973,"it doesn't matter."],[6286,6396,"All I want is you."],[7006,7106,"Hey, kiddo."],[7276,7319,"Mom!"],[7319,7379,"Hi."],[7646,7871,"I saw the news. You two were kissing."],[8103,8214,"Okay, I'm sorry, honey."],[8214,8300,"Did that make your classmates"],[8300,8416,"ask a bunch of questions?"],[8433,8517,"I don't care."],[8550,8722,"Superstar Lucas is my dad now."],[8746,8870,"So cool."],[9043,9173,"I'm gonna cook for us tonight."],[9233,9283,"Pasta?"],[9320,9393,"Double cheese!"],[9483,9602,"Double cheese it is."],[9646,9835,"It's time to celebrate."],[9835,9900,"Yes!"],[9973,10057,"Cool!"],[10086,10203,"Can't wait!"],[10313,10403,"Oh, look at my honey."]],"44":[[826,903,"What's going on?"],[1600,1755,"Lucas, explain yourself!"],[1786,2033,"You are trespassing private property."],[2043,2190,"You're dating someone?"],[2236,2429,"What about your fans?"],[2473,2626,"You betrayed us."],[2636,2831,"It's none of your business who I love."],[2900,2991,"Take her away."],[5046,5391,"Lucas, why did you give up your career for her?"],[5460,5610,"What's so good about that old woman?"],[5906,6309,"Hey, baby, sorry. It was all my fault."],[6423,6529,"Can you forgive me?"],[6609,6688,"Really?"],[6706,6768,"Yeah."],[6843,7023,"Tell me, where are you right now?"],[7066,7255,"I've been by your side all along."],[7313,7469,"I'm at the West Wind Hotel."],[8026,8245,"We need aid, move into the hotel now."],[8293,8360,"That's right."]],"45":[[223,374,"Okay, great."],[393,624,"Sir Lucas, we caught them."],[716,843,"Thank you."],[1613,1763,"Do you need any more help, sir?"],[1916,2084,"No, thanks."],[2893,2986,"Let's get straight to the point."],[3043,3142,"Break up with Lucas."],[3223,3378,"It's better for everyone."],[3433,3566,"No, I..."],[3601,3752,"I promise Lucas that I wouldn't"],[3752,3839,"give up on each other."],[4003,4159,"Then we'll terminate the contract."],[4283,4541,"Look carefully."],[4883,5016,"Eight figures"],[5079,5200,"in dollars."],[5423,5751,"Brands are lining up to terminate the contract."],[5793,5938,"The penalties will drain him."],[5993,6172,"Do you really want to see him fall?"],[6303,6416,"It's not fair. Lucas worked"],[6416,6558,"so hard to get where he is."],[6613,6823,"And it's good that you know that."],[6893,7073,"When you leave, he's still"],[7073,7458,"the golden, shining idol Lucas."],[7593,7818,"If you love him, are you willing"],[7818,7988,"to let him go bankrupt for you?"],[8096,8433,"I need to think about it."],[8516,8632,"Don't ponder too long."],[8690,8866,"The brands only give us 72 hours."],[8906,9015,"I'll wait for your call."]],"46":[[200,269,"Hey, Emily."],[306,548,"Lucas, you only belong to me!"],[813,1053,"Lucas, only you can be with me!"],[1093,1169,"It's you."],[1186,1371,"The arrest was a trick."],[1423,1523,"I'll make you understand that"],[1523,1748,"only I can love you the most in this world."],[1893,1961,"Lucas?"],[2133,2253,"It's you."],[2296,2453,"You stole my Lucas."],[2603,2834,"Now Lucas and I can be together forever!"],[3679,3797,"Let go!"],[3810,3849,"Enough!"],[3870,4033,"Lucas, be careful! She gets a knife!"],[4033,4189,"I want her out of here!"],[4366,4464,"Oh! No!"],[4464,4542,"Come with me!"],[4542,4631,"Oh! No!"],[4699,4769,"No!"],[4883,4966,"Here."],[5470,5614,"Oh my god, you're bleeding so much..."]],"47":[[123,256,"Oh my god, you're bleeding so much..."],[286,381,"Don't cry..."],[409,575,"Can we get the ambulance in here now?"],[641,769,"Help!"],[2116,2166,"Ms. Carter?"],[2243,2475,"Recent public attention is affecting the school."],[2533,2740,"Chloe will take a leave until the dust settles."],[2780,3084,"Temporary leave? For how long?"],[3153,3231,"One to two months?"],[3256,3346,"Can you pick her up today?"],[3576,3656,"Yeah, I understand."],[3663,3820,"I'm on my way."],[5006,5212,"Oh. Hey. Chloe, why are you"],[5212,5333,"standing outside by yourself?"],[5476,5640,"Nobody wants to play with me,"],[5646,5829,"and the teacher told me to go home."],[5906,6053,"Mom, I want to go home."],[6070,6152,"Okay."],[6187,6292,"Yeah, let's go home."],[8190,8327,"I've made my decision."],[8726,8858,"If I leave Lucas, will the brands"],[8858,9061,"stop the contract cancellations?"],[9136,9225,"Of course."],[9296,9456,"He'll still be the top star."],[9523,9833,"Emily, your presence is the source of his trouble."],[9833,9916,"Okay."],[10033,10120,"Now I understand."]],"48":[[723,804,"Do I look good?"],[923,1054,"Absolutely stunning."],[5713,5770,"Emily?"],[5843,5914,"Emily."],[6716,6900,"Lucas, forget me."],[6918,7129,"Take the invitation for miracle."],[7131,7320,"I believe you can do it."],[7429,7532,"Emily."],[7754,7869,"Pick up!"],[8819,8909,"Emily!"],[8923,9100,"Emily, that's not funny!"],[10238,10308,"Mom?"],[10371,10482,"Yeah, baby."],[10616,10815,"Are we really not gonna tell Lucas?"],[10826,10998,"Will he cry if he can't find us?"],[11103,11273,"No. Okay?"],[11273,11385,"So he won't cry either."],[12593,12670,"Hey! Hey! Hey!"],[12700,12776,"Can I help you?"],[12806,12947,"Did Chloe Carter arrive yet?"],[13009,13087,"Chloe Carter?"],[13133,13430,"I think her transfer was just processed last night."],[13543,13614,"Last night."],[14909,15006,"That one's so pretty."],[15033,15163,"Yeah, I can see that one, baby."],[17063,17153,"Lucas!"],[17203,17269,"Damn it."],[17443,17800,"Flight CA 1577 is now boarding."],[17923,18293,"Flight CA 1577 is now boarding."],[18506,18577,"Is that for us?"],[18596,18666,"Yeah."],[18743,18857,"That's us, babe."]],"49":[[256,355,"What is this?"],[393,471,"It stinks."],[536,699,"You plan to rot here till you die?"],[800,887,"She's gone."],[1009,1118,"What do you want from me?"],[1273,1357,"So?"],[1376,1553,"You think she'd be happy seeing you like this?"],[1866,1991,"You're gonna live like a man."],[2100,2310,"Let her see you on TV instead of the garbage pile."],[2339,2426,"What's the matter with you?"],[2453,2517,"Wake up!"],[2686,2757,"You're right."],[2846,2953,"Let her see me."],[2996,3132,"Call a press conference."],[3450,3686,"Today I am announcing two things."],[3766,4046,"First, I'm gonna star in Weber-Hopp's musical,"],[4053,4126,"the \"Miracle\"."],[4126,4528,"And second, I will donate all my profits to charity."],[4806,4984,"I will let my work speak for itself."],[5060,5248,"Time will prove everything."],[5248,5356,"One question, one question."],[5403,5569,"The evidence is conclusive."],[5600,5959,"Both are immediately terminated with"],[5959,6266,"all contractual liabilities as well."],[6552,6688,"-Well, you can't do that. -There."],[7253,7388,"This has to be fabricated."],[7433,7513,"No way."],[7526,7646,"I won't accept this."],[8000,8095,"No."],[8095,8167,"No."],[8167,8264,"-Get up. -No."]],"50":[[3,117,"Good evening, everyone,"],[117,270,"thank you so much for being here."],[303,663,"Tonight, the annual award for best album goes to"],[670,833,"Lost by Lucas."],[1056,1133,"Congratulations."],[1193,1272,"Thank you."],[1573,1795,"Thanks to my crew"],[1795,2000,"and everyone who believed in me."],[2030,2429,"This next song is for someone very important."],[2526,2743,"Without her, I wouldn't have"],[2743,2885,"been the same person I'm now"],[2885,3070,"and there would be no Lucas"],[3086,3288,"standing here in front of you."],[4266,4419,"The past month, I've turned"],[4419,4706,"my insomnia into melodies,"],[4706,4888,"my longings into lyrics."],[4923,5250,"If this song has a name, it's love."],[8153,8266,"Thank you so much, everyone,"],[8266,8439,"for being part of my journey."],[8570,8833,"I have to tell you, I'm gonna"],[8833,9059,"take a step back from the spotlight"],[9140,9349,"to follow my artistic dreams."],[9563,9731,"So Lucas, does this mean you're announcing"],[9731,9899,"your retirement from show business?"],[10096,10175,"Yes."],[10266,10353,"What?"],[10493,10716,"There are far more important things in life."],[11100,11197,"I'm here."],[11273,11406,"Just never leave me again."]],"51":[[963,1013,"Let's go."],[2060,2157,"Can you confirm the order for"],[2157,2342,"the Best Newcomer award red carpet again?"],[2376,2526,"Group A goes first."],[3563,3771,"Hello. There you are."],[3836,4202,"Honey, I am hungry."],[4316,4406,"You are always hungry."],[4566,4670,"There's popcorn popping"],[4670,4798,"in the RV if you want some."],[4820,5181,"But the popcorn is not as good as you are."],[5273,5463,"Stop teasing. I'm busy."],[5523,5769,"With what? Sitting here watching the sunset?"],[5933,6026,"That would be you."],[6056,6117,"Come on. You've been"],[6117,6379,"neglecting me since we got married."],[6440,6516,"I haven't."],[6576,6670,"It is so true."],[6773,6816,"Fine."],[7403,7512,"Is that enough?"],[7563,7676,"Mom? Dad?"],[7676,7713,"Hey, you."],[7773,7962,"Secretly kissing again?"],[8013,8144,"Not secretly."],[8190,8299,"Openly and proudly."],[8343,8503,"Well, aren't you forgetting about someone?"],[8533,8647,"What about me?"],[8696,8814,"Oh."],[9086,9173,"I love you, Mom."],[9193,9300,"I love you, babe."],[9320,9511,"-And Dad, okay? -And Dad!"],[10056,10113,"Beautiful."]]}